#: ../../../release/dev/genex-list-filter-transform-predicate.rst:2
msgid "genex-list-filter-transform-predicate"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/dev/genex-list-filter-transform-predicate.rst:4
msgid ""
"The :genex:`LIST` generator expression's ``FILTER`` and ``TRANSFORM`` "
"operations gained a ``PREDICATE`` keyword that selects items by evaluating "
"an arbitrary generator expression once per item, with ``$<_0>`` referring to "
"the current item.  ``FILTER`` also gained an explicit ``REGEX`` keyword."
msgstr ""
